OL,3,C'He's my soulmate': Pensioner's dog
OL,4,Chit by e-scooter at risk of leg
OL,5,Camputation
OL,7,FThe owner of a chihuahua, injured by
OL,8,Fan e-scooter, tells ITV Meridian's
OL,9,FChristine Alsford about the ordeal.
OL,11,FA dog owner has been warning of the
OL,12,Fdangers of electric scooters after his
OL,13,Fpet was seriously injured in Bordon.
OL,15,FMike Williams said he was walking his
OL,16,Fchihuahua, Digby, at the Deadwater
OL,17,FNature Reserve, when three young men
OL,18,Fmowed over the dog with electric
OL,19,Fscooters.
