OL,3,C'He's my soulmate': Pensioner's dog
OL,4,Chit by e-scooter at risk of leg
OL,5,Camputation
OL,7,FThe incident left 10-year-old Digby in
OL,8,Flots of pain. Two women helped Mike,
OL,9,Fwho is disabled, to carry the dog back
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,FMike is now having to rely on the
OL,13,Fkindness of his neighbours to help
OL,14,Flook after his beloved pet.
OL,16,FMike said: "It was really annoying.
OL,17,FThe kids just carried on without
OL,18,Fstopping and they damaged him so
OL,19,Fbadly. It's so upsetting. He's
OL,20,Feverything to me.
