OL,3,C'He's my soulmate': Pensioner's dog
OL,4,Chit by e-scooter at risk of leg
OL,5,Camputation
OL,7,F"He's the only thing that keeps me
OL,8,Fgoing, Digby. He's my only soul mate."
OL,10,FMike took Digby took the emergency
OL,11,Fvet, where his leg was reset following
OL,12,Fan x-ray.
OL,14,FHe has now been fitted with a splint,
OL,15,Fbut he's only allowed outdoors to
OL,16,Fexercise for 10 minutes a day.
