OL,3,C'He's my soulmate': Pensioner's dog
OL,4,Chit by e-scooter at risk of leg
OL,5,Camputation
OL,7,FMike's neighbour, Wendy Sargeant, set
OL,8,Fup a Go Fund Me page following the
OL,9,Fincident, to raise the money to pay
OL,10,Ffor the Digby's operation and a month
OL,11,Fof aftercare from the vet.
OL,13,FShe said: "We need to raise between
OL,14,Ffive and six thousand pounds.
OL,16,F"If we can't raise the money for that
OL,17,Fthen unfortunately he'll have to have
OL,18,Fhis leg amputated."
